<h2><a name="ACL"></a>ACL's Special Interest Groups</h2>


A lot of these maintain lists of more specific online resources.
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.sigdial.org/"><b>SIGdial</b></a>, ACL and ICSA's Special Interest Group on Discourse and Dialogue 
<li><a href="http://www.siggen.org/"><b>SIGGEN</b></a>, ACL's  Special Interest Group on Generation
<li> <a href="http://www.sighan.org/"><b>SIGHAN</b></a>, ACL's Special Interest Group on Chinese Language Processing
<li><a href="http://www.siglex.org/"><b>SIGLEX</b></a>, ACL's Special Interest Group on on the Lexicon
<li><a href="http://www.sigmedia.org/"><b>SIGMEDIA</b></a>, ACLs Special Interest Group on Multimedia Language Processing
<li><a href="http://ifarm.nl/signll/"><b>SIGNLL</b></a>, ACL's Special Interest Group on Natural Language Learning
<li><a href="http://parlevink.cs.utwente.nl/sigparse/"><b>SIGPARSE</b></a>, ACL's Special Interest Group on Parsing
<li><a href="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~ircs/mol/mol.html"><b>MOL</b></a>, the Association for Mathematics of Language
<li><a href="http://www.sigsem.org/"><b>SIGSEM</b></a>, Special Interest Group on Computational Semantics
</ul>



<h2><a name="INT"></a>Other international organisations</h2>

<ul>
<li> <a href="http://www.folli.org"><b>FOLLI</b></a>, the European Association for Logic, Language and Information
<li> <a href="http://www.elsnet.org"> <b>Elsnet</b></a>, the European Network of Excellence in Human Language Technologies
<li><a href="http://www.dcs.shef.ac.uk/research/ilash/iccl/"><b>ICCL</b></a>, the International Committee on Computational Linguistics. <br>Organisers of
the COLING conferences.

<li><a href="http://www.eamt.org/"> <b>EAMT</b></a>:
European Association for Machine Translation

<li><a href="http://www.ims.uni-stuttgart.de/euralex/"><b>Euralex</b></a>:
European Association for Lexicography

<li><a href="http://telri.nytud.hu/index.html"><b>TELRI</b></a>:
Trans-European Language Resources Infrastructure

<li><a href="http://www.ach.org/"><b>ACH</b></a>:
Association for Computers and the Humanities

<li><a href="http://www.tei-c.org/"><b>TEI</b></a>:
Text Encoding Initiative

<li><a href ="http://www.acm.org/sigir/"><b>SIGIR</b></a>, ACM's Special Interest Group on Information Retrieval



<li>See also <a href
="http://tangra.si.umich.edu/clair/universe-rk/html/u/db/acl/html/ORGANIZATION/"><b>this
list</b></a> hosted by the ACL NLP/CL Universe
<li>And  <a href
="http://colibri.let.uu.nl/html/organizations.html"><b>Colibri's
list</b></a> of organisations
</ul>



