<h2><a name="JOBS">Jobs</a></h2>

<ul>
<li>Job announcements from the <a href="http://www.linguistlist.org/jobsindex.html"><b>LINGUIST</b></a> List
<li><a href ="http://jobs.ac.uk"><b>Academic jobs</b></a>in the UK 
<li><a href="http://www.jobsnet.lk/"><b>JobsNet</b></a>
<li>The ACM's <a href
="http://www.acm.org/membership/career/careerline.html"><b>careerline</b></a>
contains some useful resources for job-hunting.
<li><a href="http://www.HigherCareers.com"><b>HigherCareers</b></a>
Post your resume and search for jobs in higher education,science and
research. Features jobs by email, resume search, and profiles of
universities and research institutions in the United Kingdom, Canada, Australia, United States and New Zealand. Jobs updated daily. 
</ul>

